  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This package is assigned Model Risk Level 5 reflecting a first-in-class device with no predicate, high decision consequence, and high model influence. Several credibility factors remain not-assessed without documented justification, materially weakening the overall credibility evidence at this elevated risk level.",
